snippet.title: DEAD OR ALIVE 6 Rachel Trailer
snippet.description:
Rachel the fiend hunter from the Holy Vigoor Empire returns to the DEAD 
OR ALIVE Cast soon! Rachel joins in on the Ninja Gaiden 15th Anniversary 
celebration with Momiji and is ready to take down anyone that stands in 
her way. Rachel is part of Season Pass 3 but can also be purchased 
separately on all platforms and will be available soon.

There will be costumes to unlock in game for her as well as new Command 
training, Combo Challenges and DOA Quests. Please make sure to check out 
all the playable modes with Rachel!

Debut set for Rachel will also be available which includes Happy Wedding 
Costume, Pirates of the 7 Seas Costume, Seaside Eden Costume, Summer 
Breeze Collection and Santa Bikini.

DEAD OR ALIVE 6 is available now for purchase on PlayStation 4, Xbox One 
and Steam for PC
https://teamninja-studio.com/doa6/us/products.html

Try DOA6: Core Fighters FREE!
https://teamninja-studio.com/doa6/us/corefighters.html

Keep up with the DOA6WC fighters!
https://teamninja-studio.com/doa6/us/wc_standings.html
